        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1−8. Martenseya minutocaeca n. sp., male (drawings not to scale). 1 Right antenna, frontal (setation omitted). 2–3 Tenth diplosegment (2 anterior, 3 dorsal [anterior side below]). 4 Right leg 2, anterior (setation omitted). 5–6 Gonopods (5 anterior, 6 posterior). 7 Ninth legpair, anterior (left telopodite omitted). 8 Tenth legpair, anterior (setation omitted). Scale line: 0.3 mm (1), 0.10 mm (4–6), 0.25 mm (2–3, 7–8)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4926692/files/figure.png" .

